\[\mathbf{H}=\sigma(\widetilde{\mathbf{O}})\odot\widetilde{\mathbf{H}}\;.\] (78)

This gives the parallel forward pass of the mLSTM for a full input sequence \(\bm{X}\in\mathbb{R}^{T\times d}\).

